---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Bali Encore Journeys" description="Bespoke journeys across the Three Cosmos - Nature, Culture, and Spirit. Signature journey inspirations curated for the discerning traveler.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-stone-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-stone-900/60 via-stone-900/40 to-stone-900/80 z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501179691627-eeaa65ea017c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="hero-animate text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Bali Encore Journeys</p>
      <h1 class="hero-animate hero-animate-delay-1 font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-stone-50 leading-tight">
        Bespoke Journeys Across<br/>the Three Cosmos
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Signature Journey Inspirations</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose-luxury reveal">
        <p>
          While every Bali Encore experience is uniquely designed for the individual, we have 
          curated a series of Signature Journey Inspirations. These serve as a canvas for your 
          imagination—starting points that showcase the depth of what we can create together.
        </p>
        <p>
          Explore our themes below, and let us refine them into your personal masterpiece.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pillar I: Bhur - The Untamed Archipelago -->
  <section id="bhur" class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125 reveal-scale image-reveal">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518548419970-58e3b4079ab2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-stone-900/60 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4">
            <span class="font-serif text-4xl text-gold-500">भूर्</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Pillar I — Bhur</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-2">The Untamed Archipelago</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">A Journey into the Earth</p>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-xl text-stone-300 italic">
              Before the temples and the palaces, there was the island—a landscape of fire, 
              water, and ancient green.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              The Untamed Archipelago is designed for the active traveler who seeks to reconnect 
              with the primal elements of the Earth. At Bali Encore, we view nature not as a 
              backdrop for a photo, but as a living sanctuary.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-50 mt-8 mb-4">Signature Experiences</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-500 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-50 font-medium">Volcanic Expeditions</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Private, guided treks to Bali's sacred peaks at sunrise. We bypass the crowded tourist spots to lead you to secret ridges of Mount Batur or the hidden valleys of Munduk.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-500 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-50 font-medium">Marine Conservation</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Luxury sailing and diving experiences focused on coral restoration. "Conscious Snorkeling" where we observe restoration projects and learn about Bali's marine ecosystem.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-500 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-50 font-medium">Hidden Valleys</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Off-the-beaten-path jungle trekking and river adventures in the heart of Ubud.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-500 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-50 font-medium">Regenerative Harvest</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Deep immersion into the UNESCO World Heritage Subak system. Walk through emerald terraces to meet local farmers practicing regenerative agriculture.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-sm text-gold-500 mt-6">
              <strong>ESG Touch:</strong> Carbon-neutral transport, zero-waste expedition kits, and support for local reforestation projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pillar II: Bwah - The Ancestral Trail -->
  <section id="bwah" class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 reveal">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4">
            <span class="font-serif text-4xl text-gold-600">भुवः</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Pillar II — Bwah</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-2">The Ancestral Trail</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">A Journey into the Middle World</p>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-xl text-stone-700 italic">
              History in Bali is not found in museums; it is found in the living breath 
              of our villages and the hands of our artisans.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              The Ancestral Trail is an invitation to witness the dignity, the skill, and 
              the ancient laws that still govern Balinese life today. We move away from 
              the commercial routes to enter the private courts of royalty and the secret 
              paths of the original Balinese people.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-4">Signature Experiences</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">The Spirit of the Aga</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">A trek through pristine rice terraces, entering the ancient village of Tenganan through the "forest gate" to meet local guardians of the sacred double-ikat weaving.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">The Lake of Sacred Silence</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">An immersion into the ancient rainforest of North Bali, crossing volcanic waters in hand-carved lesung canoes to discover hidden mist-shrouded temples at Tamblingan.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">Artisan Encounters</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Private sessions with master woodcarvers, weavers, and painters in their home studios.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">Culinary Heritage</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">"Farm-to-Table" dining experiences in secret locations, featuring ancient Balinese recipes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-sm text-gold-600 mt-6">
              <strong>The Difference:</strong> Expert storytelling that decodes symbols and social structures. Direct economic support for village artisans.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative h-125 order-1 lg:order-2 reveal-scale image-reveal">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555400038-63f5ba517a47?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pillar III: Swah - The Path of Awakening -->
  <section id="swah" class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125 reveal-scale image-reveal">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604999333679-b86d54738315?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4">
            <span class="font-serif text-4xl text-gold-600">स्वः</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Pillar III — Swah</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-2">The Path of Awakening</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">A Journey into the Upper World</p>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-xl text-stone-700 italic">
              In the rush of the modern world, we often lose our rhythm. The Path of 
              Awakening is a return to stillness.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              This journey is designed for the seeker who wishes to transition from a 
              "tourist" to a "soul-traveler." By stripping away the commercial layers of 
              modern wellness, we return to the core of Balinese spirituality—the realm 
              where human consciousness meets the divine.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-4">Signature Experiences</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">Sacred Water Initiation</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">A private Melukat purification at a hidden holy spring. We personally guide you through the philosophy of water and the intentional art of Balinese prayer.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">The Vibrational Reset</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Private sound-healing or meditative sessions led by authentic practitioners in secluded bamboo sanctuaries or temple courtyards.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">The Healer's Insight</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Optional consultations with authentic local Balian (healers) for traditional soul-readings and holistic wellness guidance.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-600 pl-4">
                <h4 class="text-stone-900 font-medium">Ancestral Wisdom</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">Philosophy talks on Balinese Hinduism and human consciousness with respected spiritual teachers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-sm text-gold-600 mt-6">
              <strong>The Result:</strong> A journey that leaves you transformed, not just rested. You leave Bali with renewed clarity and a soul truly "cleansed" by the authentic spirit of the island.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Weaving Together -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Integration</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-12">
          Your Journey, Your Combination
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose-luxury text-center text-stone-300 reveal">
        <p>
          You may choose one pillar as your dominant focus, or combine two or all three 
          into a holistic journey. Whether you seek the adrenaline of Bhur, the wisdom 
          of Bwah, or the stillness of Swah—we design around your intentions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Together, these three realms create an experience that touches every dimension 
          of being—physical, emotional, mental, spiritual. This is the alchemy of 
          Bali Encore: not separate experiences, but an integrated journey toward wholeness.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501179691627-eeaa65ea017c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/70"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6 reveal">
      <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Ready to Design Your Encore?</p>
      <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-8">
        The Earth Has a Rhythm
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Let us help you find your pulse within it. Your journey to Bali starts 
        with a conversation.
      </p>
      <a href="/begin" class="btn-luxury-outline">Design Your Journey</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
